Abstract = {PurposeTraumatic Brain Injury (TBI) can result in reduced social
   participation due to changes in cognition and communication. This study
   explored Instagram \#TraumaticBrainInjury posts to determine how the
   platform was being used by people with brain injury and how TBI was
   discussed.Materials and methodsExploratory, qualitatively-driven,
   mixed-methods research design. Content analysis was conducted on the top
