   multimodal resources in COVID-19 vlogs},
Journal = {DISCOURSE CONTEXT \& MEDIA},
Year = {2024},
Volume = {59},
Month = {JUN},
Abstract = {Vlogs, as one of the most popular digital genres for the construction of
