   fiction writing. My aim with fiction-based research is to create
   compelling characters situated in historical and contemporary settings
   in order to draw readers into engaging and accessible stories that help
   them learn about themselves, their understandings of others, and their
   relationships to society. I conclude with recommendations for conducting
   fiction-based research; delve into the methodology of fiction-based
