Abstract = {This article presents a Statistical Process Control (SPC) framework
   considering the response process as a unit variable, which demands
   special treatment. This study designed a Shiny app related to data
   visualization and inferential estimation adopting SPC charts and Extreme
   Value Theory. We also proposed a new flexible unit probabilistic model
