   surveillance capitalism outlined by Zuboff {[}The Age of Surveillance
   Capitalism: The Fight for the Future at the New Frontier of Power.
   London: Profile Books]. In conducting the analysis, attention is
   specifically paid to data as a `process of translation' {[}Blackman, L.
   2019. Haunted Data: Affect, Transmedia, Weird Science. London:
   Bloomsbury Academic], how the audience-participant as data-subject is
   identified and known and the ways in which data passes in and out of
