   researchers an alternative way to reflect upon and communicate their
   findings. Digital storytelling is an emerging research methodology
   increasingly used to gather qualitative data but not so often to
   communicate results. As part of the ICT4COP research project, which
   investigates community policing and police-reform in post-conflict
   settings, we decided to try out digital storytelling to communicate some
   of the findings from the research. During the process, we observed that
   the digital storytelling methodology led researchers to approach their
